{{!--
  surface-allies.hbs — Holopad Allies app.
  Companions, Factions, Contacts, Intel, Bases, and Organizations live here. Ships/vehicles are
  deliberately excluded from Bases and remain in Shipyard. Droid companions are
  visible here, while physical droid work routes to Garage.
--}}

<div class="swse-shell-surface swse-shell-surface--allies swse-allies-surface"
     data-shell-region="surface-allies"
     data-surface-id="{{vm.id}}">

  <header class="swse-allies-header">
    <div class="swse-allies-identity">
      <span class="swse-allies-led"></span>
      <div>
        <span class="swse-allies-kicker">{{localize "SWSE.ShellUI.ALLIESDATABASE"}}</span>
        <h2>{{vm.title}}</h2>
        <p>{{vm.subtitle}}</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="swse-allies-actor">
      <img src="{{vm.actorImg}}" alt="{{vm.actorName}}">
      <div>
        <span>{{localize "SWSE.ShellUI.ACTIVEPROFILE"}}</span>
        <strong>{{vm.actorName}}</strong>
      </div>
    </div>
  </header>

  <nav class="swse-allies-tabs" aria-label="{{localize 'SWSE.ShellUI.AlliesSections'}}">
    {{#each vm.tabs}}
    <button type="button"
            class="swse-allies-tab {{#if this.active}}is-active{{/if}}"
            data-allies-action="select-tab"
            data-tab-id="{{this.id}}">
      <span>{{this.label}}</span>
      <b>{{this.count}}</b>
    </button>
    {{/each}}
  </nav>

  <main class="swse-allies-body">
    {{#if (eq vm.activeTab "companions")}}
    {{#if vm.companions.hasAny}}
    <section class="swse-allies-companions">
      <div class="swse-allies-section-head">
        <div>
          <span class="swse-allies-kicker">{{localize "SWSE.ShellUI.TAB1"}}</span>
          <h3>{{localize "SWSE.ShellUI.Companions"}}</h3>
          <p>{{localize "SWSE.ShellUI.FollowersMinionsAndBeastsControlledByThisCharacter"}}</p>
        </div>
        <div class="swse-allies-section-actions">
          <div class="swse-allies-stat-pill"><b>{{vm.companions.totalCount}}</b><span>{{localize "SWSE.ShellUI.ActiveOpen"}}</span></div>
          {{#if vm.companions.historyCount}}
          <button type="button" class="swse-allies-history-toggle {{#if vm.showHistory}}is-active{{/if}}" data-allies-action="toggle-history">
            {{#if vm.showHistory}}Hide Previously Hired{{else}}Show Previously Hired{{/if}}
          </button>
          {{/if}}
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="swse-allies-drop-zone">
        {{localize "SWSE.ShellUI.GMShortcutDragANonheroicNPCActorHere"}}
      </div>

      <div class="swse-allies-lanes">
        {{> "systems/foundryvtt-swse/templates/shell/partials/surface-allies-lane.hbs"
            lane=vm.companions.followers laneId="followers" emptyText="No followers or pending follower slots."}}
        {{> "systems/foundryvtt-swse/templates/shell/partials/surface-allies-lane.hbs"
            lane=vm.companions.minions laneId="minions" emptyText="No minions or privateers linked yet."}}
        {{> "systems/foundryvtt-swse/templates/shell/partials/surface-allies-lane.hbs"
            lane=vm.companions.beasts laneId="beasts" emptyText="No beasts linked yet."}}
      </div>
    </section>
    {{/if}}
    {{/if}}

    {{#if (eq vm.activeTab "factions")}}
    <section class="swse-allies-directory swse-allies-factions">
      <div class="swse-allies-section-head">
        <div>
          <span class="swse-allies-kicker">{{localize "SWSE.ShellUI.TAB2"}}</span>
          <h3>{{localize "SWSE.ShellUI.Factions"}}</h3>
          <p>Faction relationships earned through jobs, missions, obligations, favors, and consequences. Scores can be positive or negative and benefits are assessed by the GM.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="swse-allies-section-actions">
          <button type="button" class="swse-allies-history-toggle" data-allies-action="add-faction">{{vm.factions.addLabel}}</button>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="swse-allies-base-note">
        Faction score is intentionally lightweight: record an integer score, then let the GM decide what benefits, access, hostility, or consequences that standing creates.
      </div>
      {{#if vm.factions.hasAny}}
      <div class="swse-allies-faction-list">
        {{#each vm.factions.records}}
        {{> "systems/foundryvtt-swse/templates/shell/partials/surface-allies-faction-card.hbs" faction=this}}
        {{/each}}
      </div>
      {{else}}
      <div class="swse-allies-empty">{{localize "SWSE.ShellUI.NoFactionRecordsHaveBeenAttachedToThis"}}</div>
      {{/if}}
    </section>
    {{/if}}

    {{#if (eq vm.activeTab "contacts")}}
    <section class="swse-allies-directory swse-allies-contacts-dossier">
      <div class="swse-allies-section-head">
        <div>
          <span class="swse-allies-kicker">CONTACT DOSSIERS</span>
          <h3>Contacts</h3>
          <p>Named NPC dossiers revealed through faction work, meetings, jobs, messages, and GM Intel releases.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="swse-allies-section-actions">
          <div class="swse-allies-stat-pill"><b>{{vm.contacts.totalCount}}</b><span>Known</span></div>
          <div class="swse-allies-stat-pill"><b>{{vm.contacts.actorLinkedCount}}</b><span>Actors</span></div>
          <div class="swse-allies-stat-pill"><b>{{vm.contacts.intelLinkedCount}}</b><span>Intel</span></div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="swse-allies-base-note">
        Contacts are lightweight named NPC dossiers from the GM Galactic Dossier. When the GM promotes a contact into a real actor, the actor can be opened from here.
      </div>
      {{#if vm.contacts.hasAny}}
      <div class="swse-contact-dossier-grid">
        {{#each vm.contacts.records}}
        <article class="swse-contact-dossier-card {{#if this.isHidden}}is-hidden{{/if}}" data-faction-id="{{this.factionId}}" data-contact-id="{{this.id}}">
          <header>
            <img src="{{this.image}}" alt="{{this.name}}">
            <div>
              <span>{{this.factionName}}</span>
              <h4>{{this.name}}</h4>
              <small>{{this.role}}{{#if this.factionRank}} · {{this.factionRank}}{{/if}}</small>
            </div>
            <b>{{this.revealLabel}}</b>
          </header>
          <div class="swse-contact-dossier-meta">
            <span>{{this.dispositionLabel}}</span>
            {{#if this.lastKnownLocation}}<span>{{this.lastKnownLocation}}</span>{{/if}}
            {{#if this.factionType}}<span>{{this.factionType}}</span>{{/if}}
          </div>
          <p>{{this.body}}</p>
          {{#if this.tagsLabel}}<small class="swse-contact-tags">{{this.tagsLabel}}</small>{{/if}}
          {{#if this.hasRecentIntel}}
          <div class="swse-contact-intel-links">
            <strong>Related Intel</strong>
            {{#each this.recentIntel}}
            <span>{{this.title}}</span>
            {{/each}}
          </div>
          {{/if}}
          {{#if this.agenda}}<p class="swse-contact-gm-note"><b>Agenda:</b> {{this.agenda}}</p>{{/if}}
          {{#if this.secret}}<p class="swse-contact-gm-note"><b>Secret:</b> {{this.secret}}</p>{{/if}}
          <footer>
            <span>{{this.intelCount}} contact Intel · {{this.factionIntelCount}} faction Intel</span>
            {{#if this.hasActor}}<button type="button" data-allies-action="open-contact-actor" data-actor-id="{{this.actorId}}">Open Actor</button>{{/if}}
          </footer>
        </article>
        {{/each}}
      </div>
      {{else}}
      <div class="swse-allies-empty">No named NPC contacts have been revealed to this profile yet. Contacts become visible when the GM marks them hinted, known, or compromised.</div>
      {{/if}}
    </section>
    {{/if}}

    {{#if (eq vm.activeTab "intel")}}
    <section class="swse-allies-directory swse-allies-intel-locker">
      <div class="swse-allies-section-head">
        <div>
          <span class="swse-allies-kicker">HOLONET INTEL LOCKER</span>
          <h3>Intel Locker</h3>
          <p>Player-held clues, dossiers, decrypted transmissions, rumors, and classified handouts released by the GM.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="swse-allies-section-actions">
          <div class="swse-allies-stat-pill"><b>{{vm.intel.totalCount}}</b><span>Total</span></div>
          <div class="swse-allies-stat-pill"><b>{{vm.intel.pinnedCount}}</b><span>Pinned</span></div>
          <div class="swse-allies-stat-pill"><b>{{vm.intel.encryptedCount}}</b><span>Locked</span></div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="swse-allies-base-note">
        Messenger and Secret Notes deliver Intel. This locker is the persistent workspace where players keep, pin, review, and annotate released Intel.
      </div>
      {{#if vm.intel.hasAny}}
        {{#if vm.intel.hasPinned}}
        <div class="swse-intel-locker-lane">
          <h4>Pinned Intel</h4>
          <div class="swse-intel-locker-grid">
            {{#each vm.intel.pinned}}
            <article class="swse-intel-locker-card {{#if this.encrypted}}is-encrypted{{/if}} {{#if this.isDecoded}}is-decoded{{/if}}">
              <header><span>{{this.classificationLabel}}</span><h5>{{this.title}}</h5><b>{{this.revealLabel}}</b></header>
              <p>{{this.body}}</p>
              {{#if this.hasDecryption}}
              <div class="swse-intel-codebreaker-launch">
                <button type="button" data-allies-action="open-intel-codebreaker" data-intel-id="{{this.intelId}}"><i class="fa-solid fa-terminal"></i> Open Full Codebreaker</button>
                <span>Shell-hosted console with scroll, expand, keyboard guessing, trace, and lockbox claim flow.</span>
              </div>
              <div class="swse-intel-decryption-console dx-win {{#if this.decryption.solved}}is-solved{{/if}} {{#if this.decryption.failed}}is-failed{{/if}}">
                <div class="swse-intel-decryption-hud dx-hud">
                  <span class="dx-logo">⌖</span>
                  <div><span class="dx-title">{{this.decryption.analysisLabel}} <b>LOCK</b></span><small>{{this.decryption.levelLabel}} · DC {{this.decryption.dc}}</small></div>
                  <span class="swse-intel-decryption-mode">PLAYER · DECODE</span>
                </div>
                <div class="swse-intel-decryption-status pl-status">
                  <div class="swse-intel-decryption-meter pl-meter"><div class="mlbl"><span>{{this.decryption.progressLabel}}</span><span><b>{{this.decryption.percent}}%</b></span></div><div class="pl-bar"><div class="fill" style="width:{{this.decryption.percent}}%"></div></div></div>
                  {{#if this.decryption.failEnabled}}
                  <span class="pl-chip att">{{this.decryption.failLabel}} <b>{{this.decryption.remaining}}</b></span>
                  {{else}}<span class="pl-chip">No fail state</span>{{/if}}
                  <span class="pl-chip cracked">Cracked <b>{{this.decryption.cracked}}</b>/{{this.decryption.total}}</span>
                </div>
                {{#if this.decryption.locked}}
                {{#unless this.decryption.structuralDone}}<div class="pl-manual is-warning"><b>⊞ DATASTREAM MISALIGNED</b> — pass a decryption roll to realign the transmission before the lockbox can open.</div>{{/unless}}
                <div class="swse-intel-decryption-layout pl-grid">
                  <div class="swse-intel-decryption-readout pl-main">
                    <div class="swse-intel-decryption-grid pl-readout">
                      {{#each this.decryption.tokens}}
                        {{#if (eq this.type "sep")}}{{#if this.isBreak}}<span class="swse-intel-decryption-break"></span>{{else}}<span class="swse-intel-decryption-sep pl-sep">{{this.text}}</span>{{/if}}{{else}}
                        <span class="swse-intel-decryption-word pl-word">
                          {{#each this.cells}}<button type="button" data-allies-action="select-intel-cipher" data-intel-id="{{../../intelId}}" data-cipher-letter="{{this.cipher}}" class="swse-intel-decryption-cell cell {{#if this.isKnown}}is-known known{{/if}} {{#if this.isGuess}}is-guess guess{{/if}} {{#if this.isWrongGuess}}wrong{{/if}} {{#if this.isSelected}}highlight{{/if}}"><span class="glyph">{{{this.glyphHtml}}}</span><b class="plain">{{this.plain}}</b></button>{{/each}}
                        </span>
                        {{/if}}
                      {{/each}}
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  <aside class="swse-intel-decryption-tools pl-tools">
                    <div class="dx-rail-head">◈ Slicer Console</div>
                    <div class="pl-manual"><b>{{this.decryption.analysisLabel}}</b> — {{this.decryption.actionHint}} Roll vs <b>DC {{this.decryption.dc}}</b>. {{#if this.decryption.hasSelection}}Selected glyph/fragment is targeted first.{{else}}Success targets the most common unresolved fragment.{{/if}} Beat by 10+ to resolve two.</div>
                    <div class="swse-intel-decryption-actions">
                      {{#each this.decryption.skills}}
                      <button type="button" class="pl-skill" data-allies-action="attempt-intel-decrypt" data-intel-id="{{../intelId}}" data-skill-key="{{this.key}}" data-cipher-letter="{{../decryption.selectedCipherLetter}}" {{#if this.disabled}}disabled{{/if}}><span class="sk-ico">{{this.icon}}</span><span><span class="sk-nm">{{this.label}}</span><span class="sk-sub">d20 + {{this.mod}} · DC {{../decryption.dc}}</span></span><span class="sk-mod">+{{this.mod}}</span></button>
                      {{/each}}
                    </div>
                    {{#if this.decryption.frequency.length}}
                    <div class="dx-rail-head">▦ Frequency Analysis</div>
                    <div class="pl-freq">
                      {{#each this.decryption.frequency}}<button type="button" data-allies-action="select-intel-cipher" data-intel-id="{{../intelId}}" data-cipher-letter="{{this.cipher}}" class="pl-freq-chip {{#if this.selected}}sel{{/if}}"><span class="fg">{{{this.glyphHtml}}}</span><span class="fn">×{{this.count}}</span></button>{{/each}}
                    </div>
                    {{/if}}
                    <form class="swse-intel-manual-guess pl-manual">
                      <input type="hidden" name="cipherLetter" value="{{this.decryption.selectedCipherLetter}}">
                      <label><b>Deduce by hand:</b> click a glyph, type a letter, then lock in a hypothesis.</label>
                      <div class="swse-transmission-manual-row"><input maxlength="1" name="plainLetter" placeholder="A-Z" {{#unless this.decryption.hasSelection}}disabled{{/unless}}><button type="button" data-allies-action="guess-intel-cipher" data-intel-id="{{this.intelId}}" data-cipher-letter="{{this.decryption.selectedCipherLetter}}" {{#unless this.decryption.canGuess}}disabled{{/unless}}>Guess</button><button type="button" data-allies-action="clear-intel-guess" data-intel-id="{{this.intelId}}" data-cipher-letter="{{this.decryption.selectedCipherLetter}}" {{#unless this.decryption.hasSelection}}disabled{{/unless}}>Clear</button></div>
                    </form>
                    {{#if this.decryption.log.length}}<div class="swse-intel-decryption-log pl-log">{{#each this.decryption.log}}<span class="log-entry {{this.cls}}">{{this.text}}</span>{{/each}}</div>{{/if}}
                  </aside>
                </div>
                {{else}}
                <div class="swse-intel-decryption-result dx-result-msg"><span class="lbl">{{this.decryption.recoveredLabel}}</span>{{this.decryption.decryptedText}}</div>
                {{#if this.decryption.log.length}}<div class="swse-intel-decryption-log pl-log">{{#each this.decryption.log}}<span class="log-entry {{this.cls}}">{{this.text}}</span>{{/each}}</div>{{/if}}
                {{/if}}
              </div>
              {{/if}}
              {{#if this.hasLockbox}}
              <div class="swse-intel-lockbox {{#if this.lockbox.sealed}}is-sealed{{/if}} {{#if this.lockbox.claimed}}is-claimed{{/if}}">
                <header><span>ENCRYPTED LOCKBOX</span><b>{{this.lockbox.status}}</b></header>
                {{#if this.lockbox.sealed}}
                <p>Reward payload is still sealed inside the encrypted transmission.</p>
                {{else}}
                <p>{{this.lockbox.label}} · {{this.lockbox.rewardCount}} reward payload{{#unless (eq this.lockbox.rewardCount 1)}}s{{/unless}}</p>
                {{#if this.lockbox.credits}}<span class="swse-intel-lockbox-reward">{{this.lockbox.creditsLabel}} credits</span>{{/if}}
                {{#each this.lockbox.items}}<span class="swse-intel-lockbox-reward">{{this.quantity}}x {{#if this.name}}{{this.name}}{{else}}{{this.uuid}}{{/if}}</span>{{/each}}
                {{#if this.lockbox.claimed}}<small>Claimed by {{this.lockbox.claimedByActorName}}</small>{{/if}}
                {{#if this.canClaimLockbox}}<button type="button" data-allies-action="claim-intel-lockbox" data-intel-id="{{this.intelId}}">Claim Lockbox</button>{{/if}}
                {{/if}}
              </div>
              {{/if}}
              {{#if this.hasLinks}}<div class="swse-intel-linked-chips">{{#if this.linkedFactionName}}<span>{{this.linkedFactionName}}</span>{{/if}}{{#if this.linkedContactName}}<span>{{this.linkedContactName}}</span>{{/if}}</div>{{/if}}
              {{#if this.tagsLabel}}<small>{{this.tagsLabel}}</small>{{/if}}
              <form class="swse-intel-notes-form">
                <textarea name="notes" rows="2" placeholder="Player notes, theories, leads...">{{this.notes}}</textarea>
                <div class="swse-allies-faction-actions">
                  <button type="button" data-allies-action="save-intel-notes" data-intel-id="{{this.intelId}}">Save Notes</button>
                  <button type="button" data-allies-action="unpin-intel" data-intel-id="{{this.intelId}}">Unpin</button>
                  <button type="button" data-allies-action="archive-intel" data-intel-id="{{this.intelId}}">Archive</button>
                </div>
              </form>
            </article>
            {{/each}}
          </div>
        </div>
        {{/if}}
        <div class="swse-intel-locker-lane">
          <h4>Active Intel</h4>
          <div class="swse-intel-locker-grid">
            {{#each vm.intel.active}}
            <article class="swse-intel-locker-card {{#if this.encrypted}}is-encrypted{{/if}} {{#if this.isDecoded}}is-decoded{{/if}}">
              <header><span>{{this.kindLabel}} · {{this.classificationLabel}}</span><h5>{{this.title}}</h5><b>{{this.revealLabel}}</b></header>
              <p>{{this.body}}</p>
              {{#if this.hasDecryption}}
              <div class="swse-intel-codebreaker-launch">
                <button type="button" data-allies-action="open-intel-codebreaker" data-intel-id="{{this.intelId}}"><i class="fa-solid fa-terminal"></i> Open Full Codebreaker</button>
                <span>Shell-hosted console with scroll, expand, keyboard guessing, trace, and lockbox claim flow.</span>
              </div>
              <div class="swse-intel-decryption-console dx-win {{#if this.decryption.solved}}is-solved{{/if}} {{#if this.decryption.failed}}is-failed{{/if}}">
                <div class="swse-intel-decryption-hud dx-hud">
                  <span class="dx-logo">⌖</span>
                  <div><span class="dx-title">{{this.decryption.analysisLabel}} <b>LOCK</b></span><small>{{this.decryption.levelLabel}} · DC {{this.decryption.dc}}</small></div>
                  <span class="swse-intel-decryption-mode">PLAYER · DECODE</span>
                </div>
                <div class="swse-intel-decryption-status pl-status">
                  <div class="swse-intel-decryption-meter pl-meter"><div class="mlbl"><span>{{this.decryption.progressLabel}}</span><span><b>{{this.decryption.percent}}%</b></span></div><div class="pl-bar"><div class="fill" style="width:{{this.decryption.percent}}%"></div></div></div>
                  {{#if this.decryption.failEnabled}}
                  <span class="pl-chip att">{{this.decryption.failLabel}} <b>{{this.decryption.remaining}}</b></span>
                  {{else}}<span class="pl-chip">No fail state</span>{{/if}}
                  <span class="pl-chip cracked">Cracked <b>{{this.decryption.cracked}}</b>/{{this.decryption.total}}</span>
                </div>
                {{#if this.decryption.locked}}
                {{#unless this.decryption.structuralDone}}<div class="pl-manual is-warning"><b>⊞ DATASTREAM MISALIGNED</b> — pass a decryption roll to realign the transmission before the lockbox can open.</div>{{/unless}}
                <div class="swse-intel-decryption-layout pl-grid">
                  <div class="swse-intel-decryption-readout pl-main">
                    <div class="swse-intel-decryption-grid pl-readout">
                      {{#each this.decryption.tokens}}
                        {{#if (eq this.type "sep")}}{{#if this.isBreak}}<span class="swse-intel-decryption-break"></span>{{else}}<span class="swse-intel-decryption-sep pl-sep">{{this.text}}</span>{{/if}}{{else}}
                        <span class="swse-intel-decryption-word pl-word">
                          {{#each this.cells}}<button type="button" data-allies-action="select-intel-cipher" data-intel-id="{{../../intelId}}" data-cipher-letter="{{this.cipher}}" class="swse-intel-decryption-cell cell {{#if this.isKnown}}is-known known{{/if}} {{#if this.isGuess}}is-guess guess{{/if}} {{#if this.isWrongGuess}}wrong{{/if}} {{#if this.isSelected}}highlight{{/if}}"><span class="glyph">{{{this.glyphHtml}}}</span><b class="plain">{{this.plain}}</b></button>{{/each}}
                        </span>
                        {{/if}}
                      {{/each}}
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  <aside class="swse-intel-decryption-tools pl-tools">
                    <div class="dx-rail-head">◈ Slicer Console</div>
                    <div class="pl-manual"><b>{{this.decryption.analysisLabel}}</b> — {{this.decryption.actionHint}} Roll vs <b>DC {{this.decryption.dc}}</b>. {{#if this.decryption.hasSelection}}Selected glyph/fragment is targeted first.{{else}}Success targets the most common unresolved fragment.{{/if}} Beat by 10+ to resolve two.</div>
                    <div class="swse-intel-decryption-actions">
                      {{#each this.decryption.skills}}
                      <button type="button" class="pl-skill" data-allies-action="attempt-intel-decrypt" data-intel-id="{{../intelId}}" data-skill-key="{{this.key}}" data-cipher-letter="{{../decryption.selectedCipherLetter}}" {{#if this.disabled}}disabled{{/if}}><span class="sk-ico">{{this.icon}}</span><span><span class="sk-nm">{{this.label}}</span><span class="sk-sub">d20 + {{this.mod}} · DC {{../decryption.dc}}</span></span><span class="sk-mod">+{{this.mod}}</span></button>
                      {{/each}}
                    </div>
                    {{#if this.decryption.frequency.length}}
                    <div class="dx-rail-head">▦ Frequency Analysis</div>
                    <div class="pl-freq">
                      {{#each this.decryption.frequency}}<button type="button" data-allies-action="select-intel-cipher" data-intel-id="{{../intelId}}" data-cipher-letter="{{this.cipher}}" class="pl-freq-chip {{#if this.selected}}sel{{/if}}"><span class="fg">{{{this.glyphHtml}}}</span><span class="fn">×{{this.count}}</span></button>{{/each}}
                    </div>
                    {{/if}}
                    <form class="swse-intel-manual-guess pl-manual">
                      <input type="hidden" name="cipherLetter" value="{{this.decryption.selectedCipherLetter}}">
                      <label><b>Deduce by hand:</b> click a glyph, type a letter, then lock in a hypothesis.</label>
                      <div class="swse-transmission-manual-row"><input maxlength="1" name="plainLetter" placeholder="A-Z" {{#unless this.decryption.hasSelection}}disabled{{/unless}}><button type="button" data-allies-action="guess-intel-cipher" data-intel-id="{{this.intelId}}" data-cipher-letter="{{this.decryption.selectedCipherLetter}}" {{#unless this.decryption.canGuess}}disabled{{/unless}}>Guess</button><button type="button" data-allies-action="clear-intel-guess" data-intel-id="{{this.intelId}}" data-cipher-letter="{{this.decryption.selectedCipherLetter}}" {{#unless this.decryption.hasSelection}}disabled{{/unless}}>Clear</button></div>
                    </form>
                    {{#if this.decryption.log.length}}<div class="swse-intel-decryption-log pl-log">{{#each this.decryption.log}}<span class="log-entry {{this.cls}}">{{this.text}}</span>{{/each}}</div>{{/if}}
                  </aside>
                </div>
                {{else}}
                <div class="swse-intel-decryption-result dx-result-msg"><span class="lbl">{{this.decryption.recoveredLabel}}</span>{{this.decryption.decryptedText}}</div>
                {{#if this.decryption.log.length}}<div class="swse-intel-decryption-log pl-log">{{#each this.decryption.log}}<span class="log-entry {{this.cls}}">{{this.text}}</span>{{/each}}</div>{{/if}}
                {{/if}}
              </div>
              {{/if}}
              {{#if this.hasLockbox}}
              <div class="swse-intel-lockbox {{#if this.lockbox.sealed}}is-sealed{{/if}} {{#if this.lockbox.claimed}}is-claimed{{/if}}">
                <header><span>ENCRYPTED LOCKBOX</span><b>{{this.lockbox.status}}</b></header>
                {{#if this.lockbox.sealed}}
                <p>Reward payload is still sealed inside the encrypted transmission.</p>
                {{else}}
                <p>{{this.lockbox.label}} · {{this.lockbox.rewardCount}} reward payload{{#unless (eq this.lockbox.rewardCount 1)}}s{{/unless}}</p>
                {{#if this.lockbox.credits}}<span class="swse-intel-lockbox-reward">{{this.lockbox.creditsLabel}} credits</span>{{/if}}
                {{#each this.lockbox.items}}<span class="swse-intel-lockbox-reward">{{this.quantity}}x {{#if this.name}}{{this.name}}{{else}}{{this.uuid}}{{/if}}</span>{{/each}}
                {{#if this.lockbox.claimed}}<small>Claimed by {{this.lockbox.claimedByActorName}}</small>{{/if}}
                {{#if this.canClaimLockbox}}<button type="button" data-allies-action="claim-intel-lockbox" data-intel-id="{{this.intelId}}">Claim Lockbox</button>{{/if}}
                {{/if}}
              </div>
              {{/if}}
              {{#if this.hasLinks}}<div class="swse-intel-linked-chips">{{#if this.linkedFactionName}}<span>{{this.linkedFactionName}}</span>{{/if}}{{#if this.linkedContactName}}<span>{{this.linkedContactName}}</span>{{/if}}</div>{{/if}}
              {{#if this.tagsLabel}}<small>{{this.tagsLabel}}</small>{{/if}}
              <em>Released {{this.releasedLabel}}</em>
              <form class="swse-intel-notes-form">
                <textarea name="notes" rows="2" placeholder="Player notes, theories, leads...">{{this.notes}}</textarea>
                <div class="swse-allies-faction-actions">
                  <button type="button" data-allies-action="save-intel-notes" data-intel-id="{{this.intelId}}">Save Notes</button>
                  <button type="button" data-allies-action="pin-intel" data-intel-id="{{this.intelId}}">Pin</button>
                  <button type="button" data-allies-action="review-intel" data-intel-id="{{this.intelId}}">Mark Reviewed</button>
                  <button type="button" data-allies-action="archive-intel" data-intel-id="{{this.intelId}}">Archive</button>
                </div>
              </form>
            </article>
            {{/each}}
          </div>
        </div>
        {{#if vm.intel.hasArchived}}
        <details class="swse-intel-locker-archive">
          <summary>Archived Intel ({{vm.intel.archivedCount}})</summary>
          <div class="swse-intel-locker-grid">
            {{#each vm.intel.archived}}
            <article class="swse-intel-locker-card is-archived">
              <header><span>{{this.kindLabel}}</span><h5>{{this.title}}</h5><b>Archived</b></header>
              <p>{{this.summary}}</p>
              {{#if this.hasLinks}}<div class="swse-intel-linked-chips">{{#if this.linkedFactionName}}<span>{{this.linkedFactionName}}</span>{{/if}}{{#if this.linkedContactName}}<span>{{this.linkedContactName}}</span>{{/if}}</div>{{/if}}
              <div class="swse-allies-faction-actions">
                <button type="button" data-allies-action="restore-intel" data-intel-id="{{this.intelId}}">Restore</button>
              </div>
            </article>
            {{/each}}
          </div>
        </details>
        {{/if}}
      {{else}}
      <div class="swse-allies-empty">No Intel has been released to this profile yet. Intel delivered by the GM can appear here after it is committed to the dossier.</div>
      {{/if}}
    </section>
    {{/if}}

    {{#if (eq vm.activeTab "bases")}}
    <section class="swse-allies-directory swse-allies-bases">
      <div class="swse-allies-section-head">
        <div>
          <span class="swse-allies-kicker">{{localize "SWSE.ShellUI.TAB3"}}</span>
          <h3>{{localize "SWSE.ShellUI.Bases"}}</h3>
          <p>{{localize "SWSE.ShellUI.RulesLightRecordsForSafehousesHeadquartersOutpostsApartments"}}</p>
        </div>
        <div class="swse-allies-section-actions">
          <button type="button" class="swse-allies-history-toggle" data-allies-action="add-base">{{localize "SWSE.ShellUI.AddBase"}}</button>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="swse-allies-base-note">
        {{localize "SWSE.ShellUI.TheseAreFreeformPlayerGMTextBoxesThey"}}
      </div>
      {{#if vm.bases.hasAny}}
      <div class="swse-allies-base-list">
        {{#each vm.bases.records}}
        {{> "systems/foundryvtt-swse/templates/shell/partials/surface-allies-base-card.hbs" base=this}}
        {{/each}}
      </div>
      {{else}}
      <div class="swse-allies-empty">{{localize "SWSE.ShellUI.NoBasesOrNonShipHoldingsHaveBeen"}}</div>
      {{/if}}
    </section>
    {{/if}}

    {{#if (eq vm.activeTab "organizations")}}
    <section class="swse-allies-directory swse-allies-organizations">
      <div class="swse-allies-section-head">
        <div>
          <span class="swse-allies-kicker">{{localize "SWSE.ShellUI.TAB4"}}</span>
          <h3>{{localize "SWSE.ShellUI.Organizations"}}</h3>
          <p>Natural Leader organizations are faction-like assets founded by this character. Players can describe the concept; the GM governs statistics, scale, score, bases, benefits, and privileges.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="swse-allies-section-actions">
          {{#if vm.organizations.canCreate}}
          <button type="button" class="swse-allies-history-toggle" data-allies-action="add-organization">{{localize "SWSE.ShellUI.AddOrganization"}}</button>
          {{/if}}
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="swse-allies-base-note">
        {{vm.organizations.gmControlMessage}}
        {{#unless vm.organizations.hasNaturalLeader}}<br>{{vm.organizations.lockMessage}}{{/unless}}
      </div>
      {{#if vm.organizations.hasAny}}
      <div class="swse-allies-organization-list">
        {{#each vm.organizations.records}}
        {{> "systems/foundryvtt-swse/templates/shell/partials/surface-allies-organization-card.hbs" organization=this}}
        {{/each}}
      </div>
      {{else}}
      <div class="swse-allies-empty">No organization has been recorded yet. Natural Leader characters can create the concept; the GM remains in control of scale, score, benefits, bases, and statistics.</div>
      {{/if}}
    </section>
    {{/if}}
  </main>
</div>
